data.description:
A must see. Beautiful townhome built in 2020, one owner, vacant now. Full of upgrades. Owner's gift contribution of 2% of sales price towards buyers closing cost and/or prepaids .
Ground level entrance via front door or two car garage. Downstairs offers 9-foot ceilings, 8-foot doors, two bedrooms, a small flex space and a full bathroom. Main level offers 10-foot ceilings, also 8-foot doors. A splendid gourmet kitchen with large extended granite island and stainless-steel appliances with pantry. Living/ Dining area is open to kitchen. The master bedroom is on the main level, dual sink vanities, walk in shower, walk in closet.
